msgid "Forcing the User to Re-Authenticate before Accessing certain Resources"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../security/remember_me.rst:174
msgid ""
"When the user returns to your site, they are authenticated automatically "
"based on the information stored in the remember me cookie. This allows "
"the user to access protected resources as if the user had actually "
"authenticated upon visiting the site."
msgstr ""

